# Component Patterns

## Data Editing Strategy
ALWAYS use Sheet/Drawer pattern for editing:
- Click item → Opens Sheet from right
- Sheet contains form
- Save/Cancel in Sheet footer
- NEVER use inline editing
- NEVER navigate to separate edit page
- NEVER use centered modals for forms (only for confirmations)

## Form Layout
- Single column layout
- Labels above inputs
- Error messages below inputs
- Submit button right-aligned

## Lists/Tables
- Use DataTable for >5 columns
- Use Card list for ≤5 columns or mobile
- Always show empty state
- Always show loading skeleton

## Confirmations
- Use AlertDialog for destructive actions
- Use Toast for success/info messages